You can simply ask Alexa to control your Lider smart Fan&Dimmer Switch. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our "Lider" app from Google Play or Appstore then register an account;
(2) Configure our devices in "Lider" app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3) Download Amazon "Alexa" app from Google Play or Appstore then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4) Search "Lider Smart" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5) Enable "Lider Smart" skill, and you'll be navigated to Lider Smart login page;
(6) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7) Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, turn off the bedroom fan.”
“Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
"Alexa, set bedroom fan to level 3."
